    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私に単独のお仕事が～？\nやったーうれしいっちゃ！",
      "startTime": 4.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "……わー！\n今のナシ！　聞かなかったことにして下さーい！",
      "startTime": 9.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "奥山さんのその山形弁\n久しぶりに聞いた気がするな",
      "startTime": 15.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁっ、恥ずかしいから言わないで下さい\nいつもは、出ないように気を張ってるんですけど……",
      "startTime": 21.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "ほんとーっに時々、つい油断すると\n出ちゃうんですよね～",
      "startTime": 29.166666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "無理に直さなくても。鈴村さんだって\n京都弁のままだし、いいんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 34.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんはおしとやかでプラス補正だからいいんです！\n私のは田舎者っぽいから……マイナス補正なんです",
      "startTime": 41.0000001390775,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}